<h4>Sort It Careers Expo - Year 11<br /><br /></h4>
<p><img src="https://cdn.eventfinda.co.nz/uploads/events/transformed/1234080-549929-34.png?v=2" alt="Sort It Careers Expo 2019" /></p>
<p><br />Whanganui High School has been invited to attend the Sort-It Careers EXPO at Arena Manawatu in Palmerston North, Thursday 16 May 2019.</p>
<p><span>This opportunity is targeted to Year 11 students.<br /><span id="docs-internal-guid-32754e9f-7fff-83e3-0e8a-d9863c43c5c1"><span>Year 12 and 13 get their own seminar in Whanganui.</span></span></span></p>
<p><span>An information sheet and permission slip was e-mailed to parents and students. <br /><strong>Numbers are limited so only the first 95 to sign up will get to go</strong> (2 buses).<strong><br /></strong>NB. There is also an evening session of 6.00pm-8.00pm for those who would like to go over on there own accord.</span></p>
<p><strong>Reporting time:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>11:15am at the Wanganui HS bus bay.&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Students attend pd.1&amp;2 at school</span>.<br /><strong>Returning:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3</strong>pm at the latest<br /><strong>Dress:</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SCHOOL UNIFORM<br /><strong>Transport cost:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>Free<br /><strong>Emergency contact:&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>027 278 2461<br /><strong>Supervision:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>Mr. Paul Keene (Careers Advisor), Mr. P. Turner (D.P.), Mrs. S. Crook</p>
